OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784751301
OL,3,CPotential UK wealth tax 'marvellous'
OL,4,Cnews for the Channel Islands
OL,6,FChannel Islands experts say the
OL,7,Fpotential introduction of a 'wealth
OL,8,Ftax' by new UK Prime Minister Andy
OL,9,FBurnham would benefit Guernsey and
OL,10,FJersey's economies.
OL,12,FTheir comments come amidst speculation
OL,13,Fthat introducing a wealth tax could be
OL,14,Fone of Burnham's preferred policies.
OL,16,FDuring his first speech as Prime
OL,17,FMinister, Andy Burnham pledged to
OL,18,F"help people to live well".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784751301
OL,3,CPotential UK wealth tax 'marvellous'
OL,4,Cnews for the Channel Islands
OL,6,FHe promised to immediately start
OL,7,Flaying out plans to give more people
OL,8,F"breathing space" with the cost of
OL,9,Fliving crisis - adding that detail on
OL,10,Fhow to pay for these changes will be
OL,11,Fgiven in the next few days.
OL,13,FBurnham has not detailed which
OL,14,Fspecific tax policies he is looking to
OL,15,Fpursue - however, he has committed to
OL,16,Faligning with Labour's 2024 manifesto
OL,17,Fpledges to not raise VAT, income tax,
OL,18,For national insurance.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784751301
OL,3,CPotential UK wealth tax 'marvellous'
OL,4,Cnews for the Channel Islands
OL,6,FEconomic experts have suggested the
OL,7,Fintroduction of a 'wealth tax' -
OL,8,Flevies introduced on high-value assets
OL,9,Fand individuals - could be one of the
OL,10,Foptions remaining to Burnham to raise
OL,11,Fthe necessary revenue to fund his
OL,12,Fplans.
OL,14,FBurnham himself has not ruled this out.
OL,16,FIf this kind of tax policy were
OL,17,Fintroduced in the UK, it could have a
OL,18,Fsignificant impact on the Channel
OL,19,FIslands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784751301
OL,3,CPotential UK wealth tax 'marvellous'
OL,4,Cnews for the Channel Islands
OL,6,FAs low tax jurisdictions with a
OL,7,Freputation for stability, the islands
OL,8,Fare traditionally attractive to high-
OL,9,Fnet-worth individuals - and a wealth
OL,10,Ftax could encourage more to look at
OL,11,Fthem as somewhere they might like to
OL,12,Fmove.
OL,14,FWith high-value residents contributing
OL,15,Fmillions annually to the islands'
OL,16,Feconomies, an influx could be
OL,17,Fbeneficial - as Lord Digby Jones, the
OL,18,FUK's Former Minister of State for
OL,19,FTrade and Investment, told ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784751301
OL,3,CPotential UK wealth tax 'marvellous'
OL,4,Cnews for the Channel Islands
OL,6,FLord Jones now lives in Guernsey and
OL,7,Fbelieves Burnham's introduction of a
OL,8,Fwealth tax would be "marvellous news
OL,9,Ffor introducing new wealth into
OL,10,FGuernsey and Jersey".
OL,12,F"About six months ago, a millionaire
OL,13,Fwas leaving Britain every 45 minutes.
OL,14,FTwelve billionaires left Britain
OL,15,Fwithin six months. That would only be
OL,16,Fthe start of it", he explains.
OL,18,FHowever, Lord Jones adds the islands
OL,19,Fwould be part of a "global
OL,20,Fcompetition" to attract anyone leaving
OL,21,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784751301
OL,3,CPotential UK wealth tax 'marvellous'
OL,4,Cnews for the Channel Islands
OL,6,F"The islands would have to stand up
OL,7,Fagainst the tax deals that are offered
OL,8,Fby Switzerland, Italy, Portugal", he
OL,9,Fexplains, adding "they would have
OL,10,Fstand up in a globally-competitive
OL,11,Fenvironment".
OL,13,F"Is that good for Guernsey and Jersey?
OL,14,FYes - you're at the races - but you've
OL,15,Fgot to get the ball in the net".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784751301
OL,3,CPotential UK wealth tax 'marvellous'
OL,4,Cnews for the Channel Islands
OL,6,FPaul Alker, a senior Partner at a
OL,7,FJersey wealth management company,
OL,8,Fagrees with Lord Jones, explaining:
OL,9,F"the islands' GDPs are very focused on
OL,10,Ffinancial planning and wealth advice
OL,11,Fin one form or another - so it is
OL,12,Fgoing to have a positive effect".
OL,14,FHowever, Paul adds he and his
OL,15,Fcolleagues are "trying not to
OL,16,Fspeculate at this stage".
OL,18,FSince Labour returned to power two
OL,19,Fyears ago, Paul's company has offered
OL,20,Fadvice to people looking to move their
OL,21,Fassets to the Channel Islands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784751301
OL,3,CPotential UK wealth tax 'marvellous'
OL,4,Cnews for the Channel Islands
OL,6,FHowever, Paul adds "people don't make
OL,7,Fa decision on tax alone. There's a lot
OL,8,Fof other considerations to make. For
OL,9,Fsome people, it will be very important
OL,10,F- for others, it will part of the
OL,11,Foverall decision, part of the jigsaw
OL,12,Fto put together for their future
OL,13,Ffinancial plan."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
